# Problems 2.5. Characterizing uncertainty {.unlisted .unnumbered #probs-2-5}

The models presented in the [Hurford and Watmough (2021)](https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-85053-1_11) book chapter do not contain any description of uncertainty.

- Because I am not sure how to write an `if` statement in _JAGS_, we will separate the data into _before_ the peak and _after_ the peak.

